name: SHIBGF (SHIBGF)
description: $SHIBGF (Shiba Girlfriend) is a meme-with-utility token that is already changing the landscape for women and girls entering STEM education and careers. We are officially partnered with GirlsWhoCode, and work closely with Mona Foundation and others, all of which are premiere organizations in their respected spaces with powerful Top 100 companies supporting their causes. $SHIBGF is sponsoring programs that foster female programmers and developers, and looks to grow movements to help these women thrive, both in crypto and beyond.
